1429
01:29:27,630 --> 01:29:28,800
Đúng.

1430
01:29:32,130 --> 01:29:35,260
Tử tế không hẳn
là nhàm chán đâu.

1431
01:29:35,390 --> 01:29:36,640
Như ai chứ?

1432
01:29:37,760 --> 01:29:39,260
Matt Damon?

1433
01:29:39,640 --> 01:29:40,970
Ừ.

1434
01:29:41,980 --> 01:29:43,560
